name: Mini Camera silk/cotton mix scarf
description:
Gorgeous Silk/cotton mix scarf with the classic D&D mini camera print.

Perfect Christmas present for yourself or a very good friend!

Scarf measures approx 100cm x 87cm so is nice and big and the fabric is beautiful.

55% Cotton and 45% silk so it has all the benefits of silk (handle and drape) with the ease of cotton (can sling it in the wash...carefully! on a warm or cool cycle)

2 spotty scarves in stock, if stock runs out you will be advised a lead time via email and have the option to change your mind...that's how we roll!

name: Alex Skirt - Love Bird
description:
The Alex 'Love Bird' skirt has an elasticated waist, full skirt and is knee length (54cm from waist to hem)

Each skirt is handmade to order using Duck & Duffel fabric designed in house and will take approx 1-3 weeks depending on fabric stock levels, but we will notify you of turn around when ordering. We currently have 2 skirts in stock ready to ship!

The cotton we use is 100% Kona cotton and digitally printed. 

This skirt will fit a size 8-12 but can be made in other sizes/ lengths! Please send me a message and we shall make a custom order.

name: The Perfect Clutch - Kit Box
description: Designed by Skye Pennant from blog even artichokes have hearts.co.uk "I've designed the perfect clutch around keeping your gadgets safe (the size is perfect for the i-pad mini, but could easily be adapted for a kindle etc.!), but I wanted to keep the option open for it to be used in other ways. so, I also road-tested it on a night out, and it's a great size for the essentials" This kit includes everything you need to make your own perfect clutch and would make an excellent present for a crafty friend! There is a choice of Duck & Duffel fabric with complementary lining so you are sure to find something you love. Just check out my fabric pages to see your choice in all it's glory! Please note, the kit will be sent out 'flat packed' but it is very easy to assemble the box!

name: Love birds fabric - Grey and Pink
description:
Love Birds print fabric designed in house at Duck & Duffel

100% Kona cotton. Digitally printed.

42" wide 

4.5 oz per square yard

Thread count: 60 x 60

Appropriate for quilting, appliqué, shirting, dresses, children's clothing, and home decor.

Estimated shrinkage: 2% in length and 3% in width

Machine wash warm or cool on a gentle/delicate setting, using phosphate-free detergent. We recommend washing this fabric before use.

If the amount you need is out of stock it will take approx. 2 weeks for printing and delivery, but we will let you know this when you order.
